### Hadith 4:59

*Narrated Abu Huraira:*

Allah's Apostle said, "By Him in Whose Hands my soul is! Whoever is
wounded in Allah's Cause....and Allah knows well who gets wounded in His
Cause....will come on the Day of Resurrection with his wound having the
color of blood but the scent of musk."

